<main id="content" role="main" class="group"><article role="article" class="group">

<h1>Waste Carrier Registration</h1>
<h2 class="subtitle">For a lower tier waste carrier, broker or dealer</h2>

<h2 class="registered"><%=@registration.companyName%> has been successfully registered</h2>

<p><b>Your registration number is: <%=@registration.regIdentifier%>.</b></p>

<p><b>Please make a record of your registration</b> number as you may be asked to produce it by an authorised officer.</p>

<p>Your registration will last indefinitely so does not need to be renewed but <b>you must tell us if any of your registration details change</b>, within 28 days of the change.  You can do this by going to the website <u>www.wastecarriersregistration.service.gov.uk</u> and logging in using your email and password.</p>

<div class="finish-section">
<%= render "details" %>
</div>

<p class="clr">Please use the 'Print' button to view your full registration and additional information (also sent as part of your registration email).</p>

<form action="<%=print_url(@registration.id)%>">
<p class="action group">
	<input name="finish" class="button" type="submit" value="Finish"/>
	<input type="submit" class="button-secondary" value="Print"/>
</p>
</form>


</article></main>